Package: SampleSizeSingleArmSurvival
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Sample Size for Single-Arm Survival Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mohamed", "Kamal", email = "mohamedkamalhospital@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides methods to calculate sample size for single-arm survival 
    studies using the arcsine transformation, incorporating uniform accrual 
    and exponential survival assumptions. Includes functionality for 
    detailed numerical integration and simulation.
